title: Kings Indian Fast Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Catering, Fusion
description: Indian street food restaurant, seats 60 inside. Group bookings accepted. Around 10 or so 10 dishes are vegan by default which includes 2 curries and the parantha. You could also get an Indian style vegan burger. Food is medium spiced level; mild food cannot be organized due to sauces that are already made.
